summary:
This was a drawing that I lost the motivation to finish but I still love it. 
My latest dnd character, Arten, is a elven cleric...
body:
This was a drawing that I lost the motivation to finish but I still love it.

My latest dnd character, Arten, is a elven cleric who worships the moon goddess, Selûne. She lives in the town church and practices her spells to keep her connection to her goddess strong. And peeking from behind the door is her lizardfolk mother, proud of her lil magical daughter.
